{
  "texts": [
    "(2) Different Base Models.",
    "We also explore other backbone models except for Llama with a 7b parameter scale, such as Vicuna-7b and Mistral-7b.",
    "The result suggests that our method is effective and generalizable across different pre-trained and fine-tuned models.",
    "Moreover, the performance discrepancies among them also indicate a variance in the ability of different models to absorb and utilize such structured external knowledge.",
    "Action knowledge effectively mitigates planning hallucinations."
  ]
